data.description: Charming 4-bedroom, 2 bathroom Bungalow close to the University and Downtown Lincoln!  The Covered Front porch greets you and also makes a great spot to enjoy morning coffee.  This Spacious Home has a wonderful open floor plan that boasts 3 main level bedrooms, a bedroom in the lower level, along with a Flex Room, 2 baths, beautiful wood floors, and lots of Charm and Character.  A nice size storage room awaits you in the basement and also additional storage in the Utility Room.  Store all your yard equipment in the new 10x12 Shed.  Updates Include New Furnace (2022), New Electrical Panel (2022), New Storage Shed (2016) and New water heater (2019).  A wonderful place to call home!
